description:
A DLC pack containing the Bandai Namco Collaboration Outfit set.

PAC-MAN Hat
A hat that makes you look like PAC-MAN.

DON-chan Mask
A mask that makes you look like DON-chan from Taiko no Tatsujin.

Prince Hat
A hat that makes you look like the Prince from Katamari Damacy.
name: KLONOA Phantasy Reverie Series: Bandai Namco Collaboration Outfit Set
